This paper focuses on extracting knowledgeable snippets and annotating knowledgeable documents from Web corpus, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval (IR) and deep learning (DL) techniques, which are relevant to cs.IR and cs.DL sub-categories. The paper also proposes a CNN-based model, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
